'''罗马死亡竞技场'''（{{lang-en|''Colosseum: Rome's Arena of Death''}}或 ''Colosseum: A Gladiator's Story''）是一部[[英國廣播公司電視|英國廣播公司電視]]2003年制作的[[文獻紀錄片|文獻紀錄片]]，讲述了真实人物{{le|维勒斯 (角斗士)|Verus (gladiator)|角斗士维勒斯}}在[[罗马|罗马]][[罗马斗兽场|斗兽场]]的奋斗史。

==制作==
The film was produced by the BBC in co-production with the [[Discovery_Channel|Discovery Channel]], [[France_2|France 2]] and [[Norddeutscher_Rundfunk|NDR]].

BBC History commissioned the online-game ''Gladiator: Dressed to Kill''<ref name="bbcHistory1">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/ancient/romans/launch_gms_gladiator.shtml | title=Gladiator: Dressed to Kill | accessdate=25 July 2008 | author= | last= | first= | authorlink= | coauthors= | date= | year= | month= | work= | publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] History | pages= | doi= | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108083655/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/ancient/romans/launch_gms_gladiator.shtml | archivedate=2021-01-08 | quote= | dead-url=no }}</ref> and the animation ''Colosseum: Building the Arena of Death''<ref name="bbcHistory2">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/ancient/romans/launch_ani_colosseum.shtml | title=Colosseum: Building the Arena of Death | accessdate=25 July 2008 | author= | last= | first= | authorlink= | coauthors= | date= | year= | month= | work= | publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] History | pages= | doi= | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108083658/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/ancient/romans/launch_ani_colosseum.shtml | archivedate=2021-01-08 | quote= | dead-url=no }}</ref> to tie-in with the series.

